{
  "texts": [
    "Such comments reveal the uncertainty many still feel about the longerterm impacts of AI-infused student learning.",
    "As a result, making decisions about how and if they can productively integrate generative AI into their courses still feels daunting for many instructors.",
    "More common than flat-out non-adopters were instructors who had integrated generative AI into certain aspects of their practice but not others.",
    "In some cases, they planned to expand their use of AI in the future.",
    "In other cases, they saw AI as inherently limited to assisting with specific teaching or learning tasks."
  ]
}